                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Foreign Offices of Iraq, Syria, Lebanon, Trans Jordan and Egypt, in notes to
                    American Diplomatic Missions in their respective countries, drew the attention
                    of the United States Government to <pb facs="1173" n="1159" xml:id="pg_1159"/>
                    various resolutions on Palestine approved by the Political Committee of the Arab
                    League. The notes, not printed, were of similar import and form and were
                    transmitted to the Department by the Missions at various dates between September
                    22 and October 1, 1947. A note of somewhat different character was received from
                    the Saudi Arabian Foreign Office; see telegram 431, October 15, from Jidda, <ref
                        target="#pg_1184">page 1184</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
